        <div class="ct-step"><div class="ct-num">2</div><div class="ct-step-txt">Paste your review (it's already copied!) into the Google review box.</div></div>
        <div class="ct-step"><div class="ct-num">3</div><div class="ct-step-txt">Add a cute photo of your new pup (optional) and hit Post! ⭐</div></div>
